text.tspan: Death rates from mental health and substance use disorders by age, World,
Death rates from mental health and substance use disorders by age, measured per 100,000 individuals. These include alcohol
use, drug use, and eating disorders. Figures do not include deaths resultant from suicide, which in some cases are related to
mental health and substance use disorders.
Source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease
